	&lt;li&gt;Analyzing gathered information involves using &lt;strong&gt;statistical methods&lt;/strong&gt; to derive meaningful insights and trends.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The process includes &lt;strong&gt;sorting and organizing data&lt;/strong&gt; to make it manageable and ready for further analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
